Blurb::
Discrete state variables; each defined by an integer interval

Description::
Discrete state variables defined by bounds.

The details of how to specify this discrete variable are located on the 
\ref topic-discrete_variables page.

See the \ref topic-state_variables page for details on the behavior of state
variables.

